Dialogue: 8,0:15:40.85,0:15:44.00,Text_Bottom,elena,0,0,0,fx,{\an5\pos(960,1020.1)\fscx92\fscy92\fn6CG1JR0E\3c&H00577B5C&\4c&H0092CE9B&}美也は頑張り屋さんなんだよ
